export const text = `
const list = [
    "apple",
    "banana",
    "car",
    "dress",
    "element",
    "fork",
    "grape",
    "hook",
];
<Select list={list} />
<Select label="label" list={list} color="#EF5350"/>
<Select label="label" list={list} width="12rem" />
<Select label="label" list={list} width="12rem" initValue="banana" />`;
